#: ../../source/installation.rst:2
msgid "安装"
msgstr "Installation"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:6
msgid ""
"JAnim 是一个动画库，运行在 Python 3.12 及更高版本上。用 JAnim 制作动画的过程需要编写 Python 程序，因此要求使用者对编程有一"
"定的了解"
msgstr ""
"JAnim is an animation library that runs on Python 3.12 and higher. Creating animations with JAnim requires writing Python "
"programs, so users need to have some understanding of programming"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:9
msgid "安装 JAnim"
msgstr "Installing JAnim"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:11
msgid "接下来我们介绍如何安装 JAnim，我们分为“简要说明”和“详细教程”两个版本"
msgstr ""
"We will now introduce how to install JAnim. We provide two versions: a \"brief guide\" and a \"detailed tutorial\"."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:13
msgid "如果你对 Python 及其包管理器有一定的了解，那么“简要说明”已经足够"
msgstr "If you have some knowledge of Python and its package managers, the \"brief guide\" is sufficient."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:15
msgid "而如果你是一个刚开始了解 Python 的新人，则可能需要仔细阅读“详细教程”"
msgstr "If you are new to Python, you may need to read the \"detailed tutorial\" carefully."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:23
msgid "简要说明"
msgstr "Brief Guide"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:25
msgid "只需"
msgstr "Simply run:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:27
msgid "pip install janim[gui]"
msgstr "pip install janim[gui]"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:31
msgid "不需要其它外部依赖，安装完成后运行下方命令，即可查看内置样例进一步验证安装情况"
msgstr ""
"No other external dependencies are required. After installation, run the following command to view built-in examples and "
"further verify the installation."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:33
msgid "janim examples"
msgstr "janim examples"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:37
msgid "详细教程"
msgstr "Detailed Tutorial"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:39
msgid "由于在此之后的操作或多或少要涉及到命令行操作，希望你对命令行有一定的了解"
msgstr ""
"Since subsequent operations will more or less involve command-line operations, we hope you have some understanding of the "
"command line"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:47
msgid "点击展开在 Windows 中如何打开命令行的简要说明"
msgstr "Click to expand brief instructions on opening the command line in Windows"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:53
msgid ""
"这里我们简单介绍一下打开命令行的方式，以后不再指出。在 Windows 上推荐使用自带的 Powershell， ❶简单的打开方式是 “Win 徽标"
"键 + R” 打开 “运行” 窗口，输入 ``powershell`` （Powershell 7.x 需要输入 ``pwsh``）， ❷也可以在开始菜单中输入“powershell”然"
"后回车， 或者❸在 VS Code 中按下 ``ctrl + ```。在 macOS / Linux 上一般是右键选择“终端”或者找到自带的终端图标。"
msgstr ""
"Here we briefly introduce how to open the command line, and will not mention it again later. On Windows, it is "
"recommended to use the built-in PowerShell. ❶ A simple way to open it is to press “Win logo key + R” to open the “Run” "
"window, enter ``powershell`` (PowerShell 7.x requires entering ``pwsh``), ❷ you can also enter “powershell” in the Start "
"menu and press Enter, or ❸ press ``ctrl + ``` in VS Code. On macOS / Linux, generally right-click to select “Terminal” or "
"find the built-in terminal icon."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:63
msgid "以下简单介绍几种常见的安装方法："
msgstr "The following briefly introduces several common installation methods:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:67
msgid "uv + 虚拟环境"
msgstr "uv + Virtual Environment"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:69 ../../source/installation.rst:115
msgid ""
"`uv <https://github.com/astral-sh/uv>`_ 是一套用于 Python 项目管理的工具链，目前已经相对完善，对于需要频繁使用 Python 多版"
"本和多依赖库的开发者来说很方便。官方提供了很多安装方法，可以用上文提到的包管理工具安装，也可以独立安装。"
msgstr ""
"`uv <https://github.com/astral-sh/uv>`_ is a toolchain for Python project management, currently relatively mature, and "
"convenient for developers who frequently use multiple Python versions and multiple dependency libraries. The official "
"provides many installation methods, which can be installed using the package managers mentioned above, or installed "
"independently."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:73 ../../source/installation.rst:119
msgid ""
"如果你对使用 ``uv`` 还不熟悉并略有困惑，可以 **点击上面分页中的 “Python + 全局” 切换到更为经典的安装方式**，这样你可能会更"
"容易理解，但我们仍然推荐使用 ``uv`` 进行管理"
msgstr ""
"If you are not yet familiar with using ``uv`` and are slightly confused, you can **click on the “Python + Global” tab "
"above to switch to a more classic installation method**, which you may find easier to understand, but we still recommend "
"using ``uv`` for management."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:75 ../../source/installation.rst:121
msgid "首先可以在命令行中粘贴以下脚本安装 ``uv``"
msgstr "First, paste the following script into the command line to install ``uv``"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:79 ../../source/installation.rst:125
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Windows"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:81 ../../source/installation.rst:127
msgid "powershell -ExecutionPolicy ByPass -c \"irm https://astral.sh/uv/install.ps1 | iex\""
msgstr "powershell -ExecutionPolicy ByPass -c \"irm https://astral.sh/uv/install.ps1 | iex\""

#: ../../source/installation.rst:85 ../../source/installation.rst:131
msgid "macOS 或 Linux"
msgstr "macOS or Linux"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:87 ../../source/installation.rst:133
msgid "curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh"
msgstr "curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:91 ../../source/installation.rst:137
msgid "如果你的系统中没有 ``curl``，则可以使用 ``wget``："
msgstr "If ``curl`` is not available on your system, you can use ``wget`` instead:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:93 ../../source/installation.rst:139
msgid "wget -qO- https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh"
msgstr "wget -qO- https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:97
msgid ""
"本节介绍每个文件夹下创建独立虚拟环境的方式。假如你在一个适当的文件路径（以下用 “/my/path” 指代）下，想在一个叫 “janim-"
"folder” 的文件夹下集中开发，那么请逐行运行以下命令，它会自动创建 “janim-folder” 并在其中创建虚拟环境。"
msgstr ""
"This section introduces how to create an independent virtual environment for each project folder. Suppose you are in an "
"appropriate directory (referred to as \"/my/path\" below) and want to develop in a folder named \"janim-folder\". Run the "
"following commands line by line; they will automatically create \"janim-folder\" and set up a virtual environment inside "
"it."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:99
msgid ""
"cd \"/my/path\"\n"
"uv init \"janim-folder\"\n"
"cd \"janim-folder\"\n"
"uv add janim[gui]\n"
"uv run janim --version  # 看到版本号说明安装完成"
msgstr ""
"cd \"/my/path\"\n"
"uv init \"janim-folder\"\n"
"cd \"janim-folder\"\n"
"uv add janim[gui]\n"
"uv run janim --version  # If you see the version number, the installation is complete"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:107
msgid ""
"用这种方式安装后，文档中所有 ``janim`` 指令都要换成 ``uv run janim``，如果仍然要直接调用 ``janim``，则需要先 `激活虚拟环"
"境 <https://docs.astral.sh/uv/pip/environments/#using-a-virtual-environment>`_，这是出于全局和本项目隔离的目的。"
msgstr ""
"After installing in this way, all ``janim`` commands in the documentation should be replaced with ``uv run janim``. If "
"you still want to call ``janim`` directly, you need to first `activate the virtual environment <https://docs.astral.sh/uv/"
"pip/environments/#using-a-virtual-environment>`_, which is for the purpose of isolating global and project-specific "
"environments."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:111
msgid "一切就绪后，可以使用 ``uv run janim examples`` 查看内置示例，进一步检验 JAnim 的安装情况"
msgstr ""
"Once everything is ready, you can use ``uv run janim examples`` to view built-in examples and further verify the JAnim "
"installation"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:113
msgid "uv + 全局"
msgstr "uv + Global"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:143
msgid "和在虚拟环境中安装不同的是，全局安装不需要指定用来开发项目的文件夹。"
msgstr ""
"Unlike installation in a virtual environment, global installation does not require specifying a folder for project "
"development."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:145
msgid ""
"uv tool install janim[gui]\n"
"janim --version     # 看到版本号说明安装完成"
msgstr ""
"uv tool install janim[gui]\n"
"janim --version     # If you see the version number, the installation is complete"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:152 ../../source/installation.rst:167
msgid "一切就绪后，可以使用 ``janim examples`` 查看内置示例，进一步检验 JAnim 的安装情况"
msgstr ""
"Once everything is ready, you can use ``janim examples`` to view built-in examples and further verify the JAnim "
"installation"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:154
msgid "Python + 全局"
msgstr "Python + Global"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:156
msgid ""
"Python 可以直接安装，而且多版本可以共存。访问 `Python 官网下载页 <https://www.python.org/downloads/>`_ 选择 3.12 或更高版"
"本，下载安装。"
msgstr ""
"Python can be installed directly, and multiple versions can coexist. Visit the `Python official download page <https://"
"www.python.org/downloads/>`_ and select version 3.12 or higher to download and install."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:158
msgid "使用 Python 自带的 ``pip`` 工具，会自动将依赖安装在全局。打开命令行输入该命令即可："
msgstr ""
"Using Python's built-in ``pip`` tool will automatically install dependencies globally. Open the command line and enter "
"this command:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:160
msgid ""
"pip install janim[gui]\n"
"janim --version     # 看到版本号说明安装完成"
msgstr ""
"pip install janim[gui]\n"
"janim --version     # If you see the version number, the installation is complete"

