msgid "可能出现的安装问题"
msgstr "Possible Installation Issues"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:189
msgid "安装时， ``glcontext`` 包出现以下报错："
msgstr "During installation, the ``glcontext`` package shows the following error:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:191
msgid ""
"error: Microsoft Visual C++ 14.0 or greater is required. Get it with \"Microsoft C++ Build Tools\":\n"
"https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/visual-cpp-build-tools/"
msgstr ""
"error: Microsoft Visual C++ 14.0 or greater is required. Get it with \"Microsoft C++ Build Tools\":\n"
"https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/visual-cpp-build-tools/"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:196
msgid "只需要按照他给出的链接 https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/visual-cpp-build-tools/ 下载，然后进行安装。"
msgstr ""
"Simply follow the link it provides https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/visual-cpp-build-tools/ to download and install."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:198
msgid "在安装组件时勾选 **“使用 C++ 的桌面开发”** 后点击安装按钮，如下图"
msgstr ""
"When installing components, check **“Desktop development with C++”** and click the install button, as shown in the figure "
"below"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:202
msgid "安装完成后再次尝试安装 ``JAnim`` 即可。"
msgstr "After installation is complete, try installing ``JAnim`` again."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:204
msgid "如果仍然失败，可以尝试重启终端、编辑器，或者重启电脑后再次尝试。"
msgstr "If it still fails, you can try restarting the terminal, editor, or computer and try again."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:217
msgid "额外依赖项"
msgstr "Additional Dependencies"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:219
msgid "JAnim 运作并不依赖外部程序，但是在一些少见的情况中，你可能需要安装一些额外依赖"
msgstr ""
"JAnim does not depend on external programs to run, but in some rare cases you may need to install additional dependencies."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:221
msgid "在缺少某些额外依赖项的情况下，JAnim 会给出提醒，因此在使用时不必担心，可以在遇到提示后，重新访问该页面检查"
msgstr ""
"If some additional dependencies are missing, JAnim will provide a reminder. You do not need to worry during normal use; "
"when you encounter such a reminder, you can return to this page for instructions."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:223
msgid "以下列出了可能遇到的情况："
msgstr "The following lists possible situations you may encounter:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:234
msgid "JAnim 导出 ``.mp4`` 视频时不需要外部程序，但是如果你想要尝试硬件加速，则需要安装 FFmpeg"
msgstr "JAnim does not require any external programs to export ``.mp4`` videos, but FFmpeg is required if you want to try hardware acceleration."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:240
msgid "当你运行类似这样的命令行时"
msgstr "When you run a command like this:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:242
msgid "janim write ... ... --hwaccel"
msgstr "janim write ... ... --hwaccel"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:246
msgid "可能会得到报错，提示需要安装 FFmpeg，你可以参考以下安装方式："
msgstr ""
"You may receive an error indicating that FFmpeg needs to be installed. You can refer to the following installation "
"methods:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:250
msgid "Windows + 使用包管理器（推荐）"
msgstr "Windows + Using Package Manager (Recommended)"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:252
msgid "在 Windows 系统中，一般来说会自带一个 ``Winget``，使用以下命令即可安装"
msgstr "Windows systems generally come with ``Winget`` pre-installed. You can install it using the following command:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:254
msgid "winget install ffmpeg"
msgstr "winget install ffmpeg"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:258
msgid "安装后，你需要重新命令行或 VSCode， ``ffmpeg`` 才能够正常使用，可使用以下命令检查"
msgstr ""
"After installation, you need to restart the command line or VS Code before ``ffmpeg`` can be used normally. You can check "
"it with the following command:"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:260
msgid "ffmpeg --version    # 输出版本号则安装成功"
msgstr "ffmpeg --version    # If the version number is displayed, the installation is successful"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:264
msgid ""
"如果无法使用或是对其它包管理器有所偏好，可以另行参考 `Chocolatey <https://community.chocolatey.org/>`_ 或者 `Scoop "
"<https://scoop.sh/>`_，或是 `UniGetUI <https://github.com/marticliment/UniGetUI>`_ 图形化界面"
msgstr ""
"If it is unavailable or you prefer other package managers, you can refer to `Chocolatey <https://community.chocolatey.org/"
">`_ or `Scoop <https://scoop.sh/>`_, or use the graphical interface `UniGetUI <https://github.com/marticliment/"
"UniGetUI>`_."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:266
msgid "Windows + 直接下载二进制"
msgstr "Windows + Direct Binary Download"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:268
msgid "直接下载二进制文件，需要手动处理安装位置、添加环境变量、更新二进制的问题"
msgstr ""
"Directly downloading binary files requires manually handling the installation location, adding environment variables, and "
"updating binaries."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:270
msgid ""
"可以访问 https://www.gyan.dev/ffmpeg/builds/ffmpeg-git-full.7z 下载压缩包，解压到合适的位置，并配置环境变量，这里不展开赘"
"述"
msgstr ""
"You can visit https://www.gyan.dev/ffmpeg/builds/ffmpeg-git-full.7z to download the archive, extract it to a suitable "
"location, and configure the environment variables. The details are not covered here."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:272
msgid "macOS"
msgstr "macOS"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:274
msgid "推荐使用包管理器安装，这里使用常见的 `Homebrew <https://brew.sh/>`_ 作为示例"
msgstr ""
"It is recommended to install using a package manager. Here we use the common `Homebrew <https://brew.sh/>`_ as an example"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:276
msgid "Homebrew 是 macOS 上最常用的包管理器，使用下面这个命令即可安装（如果你已经安装过了，可以跳过）："
msgstr ""
"Homebrew is the most commonly used package manager on macOS. Use the following command to install it (if you already have "
"it installed, you can skip this):"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:278
msgid "/bin/bash -c \"$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)\""
msgstr "/bin/bash -c \"$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)\""

#: ../../source/installation.rst:282
msgid "接着便可以使用 Homebrew 安装 FFmpeg"
msgstr "Then you can use Homebrew to install FFmpeg"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:284
msgid ""
"brew install ffmpeg\n"
"ffmpeg --version    # 输出版本号则安装成功"
msgstr ""
"brew install ffmpeg\n"
"ffmpeg --version    # If the version number is output, the installation is successful"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:289
msgid "Linux"
msgstr "Linux"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:291 ../../source/installation.rst:321
#, python-format
msgid ""
"考虑到使用 `类 UNIX <https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B1%BBUnix%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F>`_ 的用户一般对命令行更有了解， 而且相"
"应的发行版多，包管理没有通用的命令，这里仅给出在 Ubuntu 中的安装方法"
msgstr ""
"Considering that users of `Unix-like <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unix-like>`_ systems are generally more familiar with "
"the command line, and that there are many distributions with no universal package management command, only the "
"installation method for Ubuntu is provided here."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:294
msgid ""
"sudo apt update\n"
"sudo apt install ffmpeg\n"
"ffmpeg --version    # 输出版本号则安装成功"
msgstr ""
"sudo apt update\n"
"sudo apt install ffmpeg\n"
"ffmpeg --version    # If the version number is displayed, the installation is successful"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:300 ../../source/installation.rst:329
msgid "不同发行版包管理器不同，请自行适配"
msgstr "Package managers differ between distributions, please adapt accordingly."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:311
msgid "对于 Linux 系统，如果需要在预览界面中正常播放音频，则需要安装 ``PortAudio``"
msgstr "On Linux systems, ``PortAudio`` needs to be installed to play audio normally in the preview interface."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:317
msgid ""
"在 Linux 系统中，当你在预览界面中播放带有音频的 :class:`~.Timeline` 时，可能会遇到需要安装 ``pip install sounddevice`` 的"
"提示"
msgstr ""
"On Linux systems, when playing a :class:`~.Timeline` with audio in the preview interface, you may encounter a prompt "
"asking you to install ``pip install sounddevice``."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:319
msgid "而这个库在 Linux 系统上还需要额外的依赖 ``PortAudio``"
msgstr "This library requires the additional dependency ``PortAudio`` on Linux systems."

#: ../../source/installation.rst:324
msgid ""
"sudo apt update\n"
"sudo apt install portaudio19-dev"
msgstr ""
"sudo apt update\n"
"sudo apt install portaudio19-dev"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:341
msgid "安装 VS Code"
msgstr "Installing VS Code"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:343
msgid ""
"推荐使用 `VS Code <https://code.visualstudio.com/>`_ 进行开发，这样可以通过其中的 ``janim-toolbox`` 插件让 JAnim 的使用更"
"加方便"
msgstr ""
"It is recommended to use `VS Code <https://code.visualstudio.com/>`_ for development, which allows the ``janim-toolbox`` "
"plugin to make using JAnim more convenient"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:345
msgid "具体可以参考 :ref:`VS Code 插件 <vscode_extension>` 中的介绍"
msgstr "For details, refer to the introduction in :ref:`VS Code Extension <vscode_extension>`"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:351
msgid "请点击页面的右下角的按钮进入下一节，在之后的小节中不再赘述"
msgstr ""
"Please click the button at the bottom right of the page to proceed to the next section. This reminder will not appear in "
"subsequent sections."

#~ msgid "`FFmpeg <https://ffmpeg.org>`_ （用于输出视频文件，在 Windows 下安装需要配置 **环境变量**）"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "`FFmpeg <https://ffmpeg.org>`_ (for outputting video files, requires configuring **environment variables** when "
#~ "installing on Windows)"

#~ msgid ""
